<p>Spencer, J. D.: &quot;Cannabis Induced Psychosis,&quot;
British Journal of Addiction, 651: 369-372 (1970). </p>

<p>Sterne, J. and Ducastaing, C.: &quot;Les Arterites du Cannabis
