Dreamers,&quot; Colliers, June 4,1969. </p>

<p>Zinberg, N. E. and Weil, A. T., &quot;The Effects of Marihuana
on Human Beings,&quot; Addictions, 16 (4) : 2G-42 Winter 1969. <br>
</p>

<hr>

