<p>House Report No. 91-1444 (Part 1) 91st Cong., 2d Sess.
(September 10, 1970). </p>

<p>Idaho, &quot;Idaho State Laws,&quot; p. 98 (1927). </p>

<p>Jones, letter in U.S. Surgeon General's files to R. P. Smith
(August 21, 1920). </p>

<p>Kefauver Committee Hearings, &quot;Hearings Before the Special
Senate Committee to Investigate Organized Crime in Interstate
Commerce,&quot; 82d Cong., Ist Sess., pt. 14, exhibit 1,
119,240-241, 430-431 (1951). </p>

